---
title: Louisiana Style Chorizo Cajun Rice with Pepper, Peas and Lemon & Herb Drizzle
description: This Louisiana Style Chorizo Cajun Rice is bursting full of flavours and makes the perfect dinner night option from HelloFresh. Cook up a fresh start!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/HF_Y23_R09_W21_UK_L12614-10_Main_low-26710b52.jpg
